  "title": "Air Freight Operations Officer/ Air Export & Import Documentation Officer #81951",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Industry/ Organization Type: Logistics</li><li>Position Title: <strong>Air Freight Operations Officer/ Air Export & Import Documentation Officer</strong></li><li>Working Location: Changi Airfreight Centre</li><li>Working Hours: 5.5 days, Mon - Fri (9 AM – 6 PM) Sat (9 AM – 1 PM) (alternate Saturday upon confirmation)</li><li>Salary Package: <strong>Basic Salary + AWS + OT</strong></li><li>Duration: Permanent Role</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Prepare draft AWBs, coordinate permits before shipment arrival, and manage email communication with customers/agents.</li><li>Verify cargo details at the warehouse (pieces, weight, dimensions), update the system, and print AWB copies.</li><li>Submit required documents (FWB, FHL, permits), send pre-alerts for air export, and support cargo release/delivery and inspections when needed.</li><li>Handle customs permit declarations and submit shipment details via CCN to Singapore Customs.</li><li>Support air import/export billing and related emails.</li><li>Perform other duties as assigned.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>APPLY NOW!!!</strong></p><ul><li>Minimum GCE O-Level or equivalent.</li><li>Willing to work overtime when required.</li><li>Candidates without experience are welcome to apply; training will be provided.</li><li></li></ul><p>Kindly apply through <strong>ANY </strong>of the following methods:</p><ul><li>Submit your application by clicking the <strong>APPLY </strong>button;</li><li>Email your resume to <a href=\"mailto:Job@anradus.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Job@anradus.com.sg</a>. Please indicate <strong>#81951 </strong>on the email subject.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Anradus Application Policy:</strong> We value each application and ensure every resume is reviewed. Our process is efficient, typically concluding within <strong>3 working days</strong>. If you do not receive communication from us within this timeframe, it's likely that your application has not been shortlisted by our client. In such cases, we recommend continuing your job search to maximize your opportunities.</p><p><br /><br /></p><p>Anradus Pte Ltd | EA License No. 20C0161 | Angel Lim | EA Reg No.: R1769781</p>",
